  Locus:
    Page: 64
    Verse: 17
Tags:
  - Conscience
---
Whenever conscience speaks with a divided, uncertain, and disputed voice,
it is not the voice of God. Descend still deeper into yourself, until you
hear nothing but a clear, undivided voice, a voice which does away with
doubt and brings with it persuasion, light and serenity.
